## Setup Instructions

1. Create a new project directory
2. Create all directories:
   ```bash
   mkdir -p src/assets/{css,js,fonts,scss/{abstracts,base,components,includes,page,utils}} src/htmls public/images dist scripts
   ```
3. Create all files:
   ```bash
   touch src/assets/css/{styles.css,base.css}
   touch src/assets/js/{main.js,carousel.js,swiper-config.js}
   touch src/assets/scss/{styles.scss,base.scss,utils.scss}
   touch src/assets/scss/abstracts/{_variables.scss,_mixins.scss,_functions.scss}
   touch src/assets/scss/base/{_reset.scss,_typography.scss,_utilities.scss,_screenres.scss,_bootstrap.scss}
   touch src/assets/scss/components/{_buttons.scss,_cards.scss,_forms.scss,_carousels.scss,_heros.scss,_image-and-text.scss,_stats.scss,_typography.scss}
   touch src/assets/scss/includes/_mixins.scss
   touch src/assets/scss/page/_home.scss
   touch src/assets/scss/utils/{_filter.scss,_fonts.scss,_mixins.scss,_rem-convert.scss,_vars-bootstrap.scss,_vars-global.scss}
   touch src/htmls/index.html
   touch {.gitignore,index.html,package.json,vite.config.js,README.md}
   ```
4. Copy the boilerplate HTML content to both index.html files:
   ```bash
   # For root index.html
   cat > index.html << 'EOL'
   <!DOCTYPE html>
   <html lang="en">
   <head>
       <meta charset="UTF-8">
       <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
       <title>Project Name</title>
       <link rel="stylesheet" href="src/assets/css/base.css">
       <link rel="stylesheet" href="src/assets/css/styles.css">
   </head>
   <body>
       <div id="app">
           <!-- Your content here -->
       </div>
       <script type="module" src="src/assets/js/main.js"></script>
   </body>
   </html>
   EOL

   # For src/htmls/index.html
   cat > src/htmls/index.html << 'EOL'
   <!DOCTYPE html>
   <html lang="en">
   <head>
       <meta charset="UTF-8">
       <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
       <title>Project Name</title>
       <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/base.css">
       <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/styles.css">
   </head>
   <body>
       <div id="app">
           <!-- Your content here -->
       </div>
       <script type="module" src="../assets/js/main.js"></script>
   </body>
   </html>
   EOL
   ```
5. Initialize the project:
   ```bash
   npm init -y
   ```
6. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
7. Start development server:
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```

